> List Maybe-Str > Rex > Repl Sire
= (readRefr env rex st)
@ kids (rexKids rex)
@ rune (rexRune rex)
# switch len-kids
* _ | LEFT ({malformed reference}, rex)
* 1
    : st n < replOpen (readKey fst-kids) st
    | resolveUnqualified rex env n st
* 2
    : st m < replOpen (readModuleName fst-kids) st
